metadata.name: Long Neckie Dino PFP
metadata.description:
Long Neckie Dino is a loveable green brontosaurs dinosaur with a pink afro and exchangeable clothes. All rights to Long Neckie Dino are reserved to the creator NylaCollection LLC. Minting this NFT means you appreciate the art and/or you would like to be airdropped a burn NFT for a chance to mint your free (+gas) Long Neckie Dino Fren, of which you will have commercial rights. There are over 30k possible variations of Frens, all of which will be Brontosaurs dinosaurs with afro's.
